00:03:38,980 --> 00:03:41,430
to be is really efficient.

64
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:45,680
And the security of such a
scheme-- well, the first kind

65
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:48,780
of intuition that
we can get is well,

66
00:03:48,780 --> 00:03:51,800
if I'm a man in the
