67
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:55,740
intercepting an encrypted
message-- m prime--

68
00:03:55,740 --> 00:03:58,840
I should not be able to
get any information about m

69
00:03:58,840 --> 00:04:02,400
if I have no knowledge
